   3905          /***************************************************************************//**
   3906           * @brief
   3907           *   Configure wait state settings necessary to switch to a given core clock
   3908           *   frequency at a certain voltage scale level.
   3909           *
   3910           * @details
   3911           *   This function will set up the necessary flash wait states. Updating the
   3912           *   wait state configuration must be done before increasing the clock
   3913           *   frequency and it must be done after decreasing the clock frequency.
   3914           *   Updating the wait state configuration must be done before core voltage is
   3915           *   decreased and it must be done after a core voltage is increased.
   3916           *
   3917           * @param[in] freq
